<li> May [loved one's name]'s spirit live on in your heart.</li>
<li> Remember the beautiful life [loved one's name] lived.</li>
<li> Cherish the precious memories you shared with [loved one's name].</li>
<li> Holding you and [loved one's name]'s memory close to my heart.</li>
<li> May [loved one's name] rest in peace.</li>
<li> Thinking of you and [loved one's name]. May your memories bring you comfort.</li>
<li> May beautiful memories of [loved one's name] shine brightly in your heart.</li>
