<p>As time goes on, the focus shifts towards healing and remembrance. These messages offer hope and encouragement for the future.</p>
<li>Though grief is profound, healing is possible.  Take all the time you need.</li>
<li> May the memories of [loved one's name] bring you comfort and joy in the days to come.</li>
<li> May peace and serenity guide you through this time of grief.</li>
<li> Even in sadness, there is hope and strength to be found.</li>
